## 2. Core SEO Components

### SEOMetadata.tsx
```typescript
interface SEOMetadataProps {
  title: string;
  description: string;
  canonical?: string;
  ogImage?: string;
  keywords?: string[];
  noindex?: boolean;
}

// Component should:
// - Use react-helmet-async for meta tag management
// - Include Open Graph tags for social sharing
// - Add Twitter Card meta tags
// - Implement canonical URL logic
// - Support location-specific meta data
```

### SchemaInjector.tsx
```typescript
interface SchemaInjectorProps {
  type: 'LocalBusiness' | 'Service' | 'FAQPage' | 'Article';
  data: Record<string, any>;
}

// Component should inject JSON-LD structured data for:
// - LocalBusiness with full NAP + service area
// - Service schema for Starlink installation
// - FAQPage for location-specific FAQs
// - BreadcrumbList for navigation
```

