## 4. Homepage Components Priority

### HeroSection.tsx Features
- Headline: "DMV's #1 Rated Starlink Installation Experts"
- Subheadline addressing pain point: "Escape Slow Internet Forever"
- Dual CTAs: "Get Free Quote" (primary) + "Check Availability" (secondary)
- Social proof: "500+ Installations | 4.9★ Rating | Same-Day Service"
- Background: Subtle gradient with tech pattern

### ServiceComparison.tsx
```typescript
// Three-column comparison table:
// Column 1: "DIY Installation" (problems/risks)
// Column 2: "National Installers" (generic/slow)
// Column 3: "The Orbit Tech" (professional/local/fast)
// 
// Emphasize local expertise and rapid response
```

### TrustIndicators.tsx
- Google Reviews integration (4.9★ with count)
- "Certified Starlink Installer" badge
- "Fully Insured & Licensed" badge
- "2-Year Service Warranty" badge
- Installation counter (animated number)

