## 7. Technical Implementation Standards

### TypeScript Interfaces
```typescript
// Location Data Structure
interface Location {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  county: string;
  state: 'VA' | 'MD' | 'DC';
  population: number;
  serviceAreas: string[];
  testimonials: Testimonial[];
  faqs: FAQ[];
  schema: LocalBusinessSchema;
}

// Testimonial Structure
interface Testimonial {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  location: string;
  rating: number;
  date: string;
  content: string;
  speedBefore?: number;
  speedAfter?: number;
  verified: boolean;
}

// Pricing Structure
interface PricingPackage {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  price: number;
  features: string[];
  highlighted: boolean;
  ctaText: string;
}
```

### Tailwind Configuration
```javascript
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        primary: {
          50: '#f0f9ff',
          500: '#3b82f6',
          600: '#2563eb',
          700: '#1d4ed8',
          800: '#1e40af',
          900: '#1e3a8a',
        },
        dark: {
          900: '#0f172a',
          800: '#1e293b',
          700: '#334155',
        },
        accent: {
          500: '#10b981', // Success green for CTAs
        }
      },
      fontFamily: {
        sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
      },
      animation: {
        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out',
        'slide-up': 'slideUp 0.4s ease-out',
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Performance Optimization Checklist
- [ ] Implement lazy loading for below-fold images
- [ ] Use `loading="eager"` for above-fold hero image
- [ ] Minify and compress all images (WebP format)
- [ ] Implement route-based code splitting
- [ ] Add resource hints (`<link rel="preconnect">`)
- [ ] Enable Vite build optimizations
- [ ] Implement 3-second load time target
- [ ] Add Core Web Vitals monitoring

