## 8. Analytics & Tracking Setup

### Google Tag Manager Events
```javascript
// Track these events:
dataLayer.push({
  event: 'lead_form_submit',
  form_type: 'quick_quote',
  service_selected: 'starlink_installation',
  location: 'loudoun_county'
});

dataLayer.push({
  event: 'phone_click',
  click_location: 'header',
  phone_number: '703XXXXXXX'
});

dataLayer.push({
  event: 'cta_click',
  button_text: 'Get Free Quote',
  page_section: 'hero'
});
```

### Conversion Goals
1. Primary: Lead form submissions
2. Secondary: Phone calls (tracked)
3. Micro: Email clicks
4. Engagement: Time on location pages (>2 min)
5. Navigation: Service area checker usage

---

## 9. Launch Sequence & Priorities

### Week 1: Foundation
1. Set up project structure and dependencies
2. Implement SEOMetadata and SchemaInjector components
3. Create responsive Layout with Header/Footer
4. Deploy basic homepage with hero and CTAs

### Week 2: Location Pages
1. Create location page template
2. Launch Loudoun County page (highest search volume)
3. Launch Fairfax County page
4. Implement local schema markup
5. Submit updated sitemap to Google

### Week 3: Conversion Optimization
1. Implement multi-step lead form
2. Add phone tracking
3. Create thank you page with pixel tracking
4. Set up Google Tag Manager events
5. A/B test CTA button colors

### Week 4: Content & Authority
1. Publish pillar "Ultimate Guide" blog post
2. Create and optimize Google Business Profile
3. Add testimonials and case studies
4. Implement FAQ schema
5. Begin link building outreach

---

## 10. Quality Assurance Checklist

### Pre-Launch Testing
- [ ] Mobile responsiveness (iPhone, Android)
- [ ] Cross-browser testing (Chrome, Safari, Firefox, Edge)
- [ ] Form submission and email delivery
- [ ] Phone click-to-call functionality
- [ ] Page speed <3 seconds (Google PageSpeed Insights)
- [ ] All meta tags populated correctly
- [ ] Schema markup validates (Google Rich Results Test)
- [ ] Analytics tracking fires correctly
- [ ] 404 page configured
- [ ] SSL certificate active
- [ ] Robots.txt and sitemap.xml configured

### SEO Launch Checklist
- [ ] Submit sitemap to Google Search Console
- [ ] Submit sitemap to Bing Webmaster Tools
- [ ] Verify Google Business Profile
- [ ] Set up local citations (Yelp, etc.)
- [ ] Configure Google Analytics 4
- [ ] Set up conversion tracking
- [ ] Implement heat mapping (Hotjar/Clarity)
- [ ] Create first month content calendar
- [ ] Document keyword ranking baselines

